OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Schools in Wales    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstill face chaos, teachers 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fwarn                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disruption caused by Covid in schools  
OL,6, is as bad as it has been at any point  
OL,7, over the pandemic, teachers have said. 
OL,9,FOne union described the situation as   
OL,10,F"chaotic" and "stressful" as schools   
OL,11,Fstruggle to plug staffing gaps.        
OL,13,FIt has led to calls on the Welsh       
OL,14,Fgovernment to extend asymptomatic      
OL,15,Ftesting of staff and provide extra     
OL,16,Ffunding for supply teachers.           
OL,18,FEducation Minister Jeremy Miles said   
OL,19,Fthe Welsh government was trying to help
OL,20,Falleviate staffing pressures.          
